review: Victoria's place was clean and she was great with communication. I recommend her place to anyone needing a spot close to the airport.
Victoria’s place is a charming place! A great location, clean, spacious and yes...the suitcase stand is great!

Victoria is very kind and accommodating. I so appreciated the fact that she has a luggage rack in the room. Such a seemingly small thing yet oh-so-useful that most, if not all, of the places I’ve stayed at do not have.
Everything was great, very simple, easy for my quick overnight trip. Victoria graciously dropped me off at the airport the following morning on her way out. 5 stars all the way around!
Victoria was very nice. Picked me up and dropped me off at the airport with a small charge. She also had coffee ready or me in the morning!!
Victoria is a wonderful host! Comfortable bed ! Wish I didn't have to leave early but the nature of my work... will be back next time I go to Houston.

Great location and clean amenities. We came for the MotoGP races and it was perfect for what we needed. There were roadrunners everywhere which was awesome! We would definitely return next year if the house is available.

Gary and Connie were great hosts and their place is spectacular. Plenty of room as there was 4 grown men in our party. 15 minutes from Lake Bastrop and 45 minutes from Lake Fayette. Awesome Bass lakes. Already talking about our next trip down there.
